Webhooks:-
# Setting up a webhook endpoint to receive events from Stripe
Go to Stripe Dashboard → Developers → Webhooks

Link: https://dashboard.stripe.com/test/webhooks

https://abcd1234.ngrok.io/webhook


Under Events to send, you can select specific ones like:

payment_intent.succeeded

payment_intent.payment_failed

charge.succeeded
(Or just "Send all events" for testing.)

Click “Add endpoint”


For Webhook you can download and install from https://docs.stripe.com/stripe-cli/install

Then run the following command in terminal to forward events to your local server:


Run : ngrok http 4242







